{"about_the_game":"If you are a fan of the <i>Resident Evil</i> series and pixel art graphics, this is your game: <strong><i>Desolate City: Last Show</i></strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STORY</h2>It's the final concert of his tour. Don Aitor is on stage, killing it. Suddenly, people start acting strangely, and chaos ensues. Now he must survive the horror and uncover the consequences of the strange virus that is threatening the pixelated city of Gray Bay. This video game serves as a prequel to <strong><i>Desolate City: The Bloody Dawn</i></strong>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687960/extras/gunresize.gif?t=1718126058\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAMEPLAY</h2>Our protagonist will need to trade the microphone for a different type of weaponry to defend himself.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<strong>Melee Weapons</strong>: Decide whether you want to save ammunition by risking getting too close to the maniacs.[]<strong>Firearms</strong>: Shoot from a distance, eliminate enemies, and blow heads off.[]<strong>Limited Ammo &amp; Healing Items</strong>: You'll have to carefully consider whether it's worth shooting or opt for dodging. Saves are also limited, so you need to be cautious.[]<strong>Quick Menu &amp; Inventory</strong>: Switch weapons instantly with the quick menu or manage your inventory calmly from the menu.[]<strong>Survivors</strong>: Find survivors, interact with them, and rescue them from life-or-death situations.[]<strong>Old-School Flavor</strong>: Solve puzzles, find keys to access new areas, and read documents to learn more details about the story.<li><strong>Integrated achievements</strong>: The game incorporates its own achievement system.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687960/extras/menuresize.gif?t=1718126058\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PIXEL ART</h2><strong>Desolate City: Last Show</strong> features beautiful hand-drawn pixel art and carefully crafted illustrations to explain the game's story.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ORIGINAL SOUNDTRACK</h2>Enjoy terrifying tracks and songs performed by the protagonist of the story, <strong>Don Aitor</strong>, narrating the events of the game. You can find the videogame's main song and music video on youtube, it's titled <strong>&quot;Don Aitor - La \u00faltima funci\u00f3n&quot;</strong> (turn the english subtitles on). It's a rap song performed by Don Aitor featuring a opera singer/soprano girl. Amazing!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687960/extras/ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1718126058\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687960/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1718126058","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687960/page.bg.jpg?t=1718126058","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687960/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1718126058","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687960/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1718126058","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"The game contains blood, gunfire, corpses and stabbings (all depicted in pixel art)."},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"If you are a fan of the <i>Resident Evil</i> series and pixel art graphics, this is your game: <strong><i>Desolate City: Last Show</i></strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STORY</h2>It's the final concert of his tour. Don Aitor is on stage, killing it. Suddenly, people start acting strangely, and chaos ensues. Now he must survive the horror and uncover the consequences of the strange virus that is threatening the pixelated city of Gray Bay. This v